<!-- Terms & Conditions Modal -->
<div class="v10-modal-overlay" id="terms-modal" style="display: none;">
  <div class="v10-modal v10-modal--terms">
    <div class="v10-modal-header">
      <div class="v10-modal-icon v10-modal-icon--info">
        <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
          <path d="M12 16v-4"/>
          <path d="M12 8h.01"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="v10-modal-title">Terms & Conditions</h3>
      <button type="button" class="v10-modal-close" aria-label="Close">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path d="M15 5L5 15M5 5l10 10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
        </svg>
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="v10-modal-body">
      <div class="terms-content">
        <h4>1. Service Agreement</h4>
        <p>By submitting a request through our TechPack system, you agree to our terms of service and manufacturing agreements. All specifications provided will be used to create samples or fulfill orders as requested.</p>
        
        <h4>2. Pricing & Payment</h4>
        <p>All prices displayed are estimates and may vary based on final specifications. Sample payments are required upfront. Bulk order deposits are required upon order confirmation.</p>
        
        <h4>3. Production Times</h4>
        <p>Sample production: 7-14 business days. Bulk orders: 15-30 business days depending on quantity and complexity. Rush orders may be available for additional fees.</p>
        
        <h4>4. Quality Standards</h4>
        <p>We maintain high quality standards for all products. Any quality issues must be reported within 48 hours of delivery for resolution.</p>
        
        <h4>5. Intellectual Property</h4>
        <p>You retain ownership of your designs. We will not reproduce your designs for other clients without permission. All uploaded files are confidential.</p>
        
        <h4>6. Cancellation Policy</h4>
        <p>Samples: Cancellations accepted within 24 hours of order placement. Bulk orders: Cancellations accepted before production begins (typically within 48 hours).</p>
        
        <h4>7. Shipping & Returns</h4>
        <p>Shipping costs are additional unless otherwise specified. Returns are accepted for defective items only. Custom items are non-returnable unless defective.</p>
        
        <h4>8. Contact Information</h4>
        <p>For questions about these terms, contact us at support@genuineblanks.com or through our customer service portal.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="v10-modal-actions">
      <button type="button" class="v10-btn v10-btn--primary v10-modal-close">I Understand</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

